PACIFIC OILCLOTH & LINOLEUM CO., Appellant, v. Wm. C. McDUFFIE, as Receiver of Richfield Oil Company, Appellee. No. 7346. . Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Feb. 21, 1934. John B. Haas and John D. Home, both of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Gibson, Dunn & Crutcher and David P. Evans, all of Los Angeles, Cal., for appel-lee.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

After oral argument of counsel for re-speetive parties, ordered orders of District Court affirmed; mandate forthwith.
